Importance of Readability

Anyone who is into programming knows the Importance of formatting the code for Readability.
The teraform fmt command is used to  rewrite Terraform confi files to take care of the overall formatting.


command is terraform fmt

before fmt
resource        "aws_instance" "ec2-terraform-as3-1" {
  ami      = "ami-0bdd88bd06d16ba03"
  instance_type =                  "t3.micro"

}


after fmt

resource "aws_instance" "ec2-terraform-as3-1" {
  ami           = "ami-0bdd88bd06d16ba03"
  instance_type = "t3.micro"

}